nct exit codes, no model call. Report #6: the b3e5 idempotence short-circuit sets coverage.idempotent_skip but _render_plan_review_text shows an identical PASS with no marker — render a 'reused (cached)' line. AC: --status makes no model call; text output distinguishes a reused verdict; tests for both.","env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","file_impact":[],"keyring":[],"last_status_env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","managed_refs":[["parent","29c2-19c0-2b67-47de"]],"parent_id":"29c2-19c0-2b67-47de","parent_status_uuid":"61a64b7c-646d-4f22-8493-3f598c29e657","plan_review_phase":"execution","preconditions_summary":{"status":"pre-manifest"},"priority":2,"reverts":[],"status":"in_progress","tags":[],"ticket_id":"9603-f939-f162-4aa7","ticket_type":"story","title":"Add read-only, no-LLM `review-plan --status` currency query + surface idempotent-skip in text (#2,#6)","verify_commands":[]},"source_event_uuids":["ced70b3e-17d2-4ca8-b713-a198d6f7bbcb","47302a95-d937-4e3e-ba1d-1cfc2aa93a39","61a64b7c-646d-4f22-8493-3f598c29e657","8704f589-d57d-4991-a5a2-95dec8f45852","d98b4789-408f-4433-ae71-05827457d570","a94c6cce-0398-42ef-b047-482970bebd9a","0a0c758c-dd1c-419b-a61a-6548921d94d5"]},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"SNAPSHOT","timestamp":1784753738181236002,"uuid":"c425281f-5efd-40e0-bc2c-42d129c323fb"}